Package views

package views
The views package contains classes that provide various output for the SC2002_CAMs application.
Since:
1.0
Version:
1.0

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CampDetailView
    The CampDetailView class provides a view for displaying detailed information about a camp, specifically the camp currently facilitated by the committee member logged in.
    CommitteeEnquiryView
    The CommitteeEnquiryView class provides functionality to view enquiries related to a specific camp.
    CommitteeSuggestionView
    The CommitteeSuggestionView class provides functionality to view suggestions made for a specific camp by the current committee member.
    CreatedCampView
    The CreatedCampView class provides a view for staff to see all camps they have created.
    ProfileView
    The ProfileView class provides a view to display the user profile information.
    RegisteredCampView
    The RegisteredCampView class provides a view to display the list of camps that a student is registered for.
    StaffAllCampView
    The StaffAllCampView class provides a view for staff to see a list of all camps.
    StaffEnquiryView
    The StaffEnquiryView class provides functionality to view enquiries made for the camps created by the current staff member.
    StaffSuggestionView
    The StaffSuggestionView class provides functionality to view suggestions made for the camps created by the current staff member.
    StudentAllCampView
    The StudentAllCampView class provides a view for students to see all available camps.
    StudentEnquiryView
    The StudentEnquiryView class provides a view for students to see their enquiries.
